'''Ayrou''' was the language used by the [[Ayrou/Legends|Ayrou]] [[Species/Legends|species]]. It was described by [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]]-speakers as "a trilling shriek that could be made by strangling a songbird."<ref name="u">''[[Ultimate Alien Anthology]]''</ref>

